highlights.text: Juice WRLD has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Smile (with The Weeknd)” is the highest at #9.
“Mood (feat. iann dior)” by 24kGoldn and iann dior is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 122 spots at #37.
“Laugh Now Cry Later (feat. Lil Durk)” by Drake and Lil Durk is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 189 weeks straight.
